headline: Why investors should avoid 'over-risking' in equities right now
summary: Wells Fargo's (WFC) Investment Institute released its 2025 mid-year outlook last week, offering insights for investors. Veronica Willis, Wells Fargo Investment Institute global investment strategist, joins Morning Brief to explain the report's findings, why investors should stay positioned in small-cap and mid-cap equities, and where she's seeing opportunity. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Morning Brief here.
